            {
              "content": "=Here are some recent topics already covered: {{ $json.recentIdeas }}\n\nGenerate ONE new, specific, non-generic social media content idea related to technology, career growth, or productivity. It must be meaningfully different in substance from typical recycled topics, not just reworded.\n\nThe idea MUST be written in English.\n\nReturn ONLY the idea as plain text in English, nothing else."
